# LLM Configuration
# =================
# Modify this file to point to your own LLM endpoint.
# The toolkit uses LangChain's ChatOpenAI interface, which is compatible
# with any OpenAI-compatible API (Azure OpenAI, vLLM, Ollama, etc.).

# To use your own endpoint, set these environment variables in a .env file:
#   OPENAI_API_KEY=your-api-key
#   OPENAI_API_BASE=https://your-endpoint.com/v1
#   LLM_MODEL_NAME=gpt-4o-mini
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
OPENAI_API_BASE=https://api.openai.com/v1
LLM_MODEL_NAME=gpt-4o-mini
